Generic single-database configuration.

This is a database migration tool
If you change tables in the database, you can use this tool to update the database schema.

[Documentation](https://alembic.sqlalchemy.org/en/latest/api/ddl.html)


# How to use
`alembic upgrade head` - upgrade to the latest migration
`alembic revision --autogenerate -m "message"` - create a new migration
`alembic upgrade +1` - upgrade 1 migration
`alembic downgrade -1` - rollback 1 migration